metadata.name: French Roast Felix from the Caffeine Claws Club
metadata.description:
A collection of 20 animated cats who understand the struggle of a bad hair day and a restless night of bad dreams. But fear not, because they know the ultimate remedy - a good cup of coffee!

Join these caffeinated kitties as they crave that energizing brew to kickstart their day and tame their unruly fur. From lattes to cappuccinos, these feline friends know their coffee and won't let anything stand in the way of their morning fix.

Whether you're a coffee lover or a cat lover (or both!), "Morning Fluffs" is the perfect addition to your morning routine. So grab your own cup of joe and enjoy the company of these animated cats as they conquer bad hair days and bad dreams one sip at a time.

Cheers to a purrfect morning!
